{"tid":2406774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來張宇人好黃","createTime":"2021-02-13T13:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T10:49:36.000Z","uid":113951,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ec18b772321cadab2a1eec5f08dbccad9fbe00","tid":2406774,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"到底廿蚊張知唔知自己講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//行會成員反對政府措施 <br />\n  自由黨張宇人在電台節目呼籲，餐廳應該拒絕要求手寫登記的客人用餐，並告知「明天請早」。如此事屬實，筆者想警告張宇人議員小心言行。<br />\n <br />\n 身為行會成員，在情在理，都應該支持政府施政。然而張宇人竟然公開在電台反對特區政府措施，公開呼籲餐廳抵制政府電子和紙本登記的雙軌制度，煽動餐廳只接受單一形式記錄訪客。 <br />\n<br />\n 如果餐廳不慎聽從此一用心險害的言論，隨時會令一眾不了解「安心出行」高科技的市民，到外用膳時諸多不便。到時老人家落街連茶都冇得飲，齊聲在門外詛咒特區官員冚家剷，真是陷林鄭於不義呀。 <br />\n<br />\n 可能事後記者朋友都知佢語無倫次，有關言論似乎未見寫在之後的文字報導中，未知是否應他要求不寫了。//<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6027cb157e8cc57c1898629a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F6027cb157e8cc57c1898629a&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=adc2b57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6027cb157e8cc57c1898629a</a>"},{"pid":"175303cbcbc10f71406dff2f7315aea80e7d5667","tid":2406774,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"咪係囉 成班傻西又話罷食太興敏華"},{"pid":"3d69bba080c3d82dbb03dd064edfb25cede8de9d","tid":2406774,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9ec18b772321cadab2a1eec5f08dbccad9fbe00","tid":2406774,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"到底廿蚊張知唔知自己講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//行會成員反對政府措施 <br />\n  自由黨張宇人在電台節目呼籲，餐廳應該拒絕要求手寫登記的客人用餐，並告知「明天請早」。如此事屬實，筆者想警告張宇人議員小心言行。<br />\n <br />\n 身為行會成員，在情在理，都應該支持政府施政。然而張宇人竟然公開在電台反對特區政府措施，公開呼籲餐廳抵制政府電子和紙本登記的雙軌制度，煽動餐廳只接受單一形式記錄訪客。 <br />\n<br />\n 如果餐廳不慎聽從此一用心險害的言論，隨時會令一眾不了解「安心出行」高科技的市民，到外用膳時諸多不便。到時老人家落街連茶都冇得飲，齊聲在門外詛咒特區官員冚家剷，真是陷林鄭於不義呀。 <br />\n<br />\n 可能事後記者朋友都知佢語無倫次，有關言論似乎未見寫在之後的文字報導中，未知是否應他要求不寫了。//<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6027cb157e8cc57c1898629a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F6027cb157e8cc57c1898629a&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=adc2b57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6027cb157e8cc57c1898629a</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"推一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}